videos.description: Off of Keith Williams' missed 3-pointer, Tre Scott battles for an offensive rebound and rises up for a two-handed slam.

videos.description: Cincinnati's Jarron Cumberland drives to the rim, finishes in traffic and shushes the UCF crowd on his way back down the court.
